<p class="p1"><b>Using Tutorial Simple as Starting Code</b></p>
<p class="p2">Changes need if using <b>Tutorial-Frontend-Vue3-Simple</b> as starting code</p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Change the path for backend request.</li>
</ul>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Find src/services/services.js</li>
  <li class="li2">Update the baseurl for dev and prod.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Change “tutorial-simple” to a new baseurl for the REST request for the new project.</li>
</ul>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1">var</span><span class="s2"> </span>baseurl<span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">=</span><span class="s2"> </span><span class="s4">""</span><span class="s2">;</span></p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s5">if</span> (<span class="s5">import</span>.<span class="s6">meta</span>.<span class="s6">env</span>.<span class="s7">DEV</span>) {</p>
<p class="p5"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></span><span class="s6">baseurl</span><span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">=</span><span class="s2"> </span>"http://localhost/tutorial-simple"<span class="s2">;</span></p>
<p class="p4">} <span class="s5">else</span> {</p>
<p class="p5"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></span><span class="s6">baseurl</span><span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">=</span><span class="s2"> </span>"/tutorial-simple"<span class="s2">;</span></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Add a ProxyPass line in the Apache config file with the new baseurl for the REST requests to the backend.</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Find the ProxyPass set of lines in the Apache config file and add a new line replacing tutorial-simple (twice) with the new baseurl.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Also update 3101 to the port you are using for the backend.</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p7">ProxyPass /tutorial-simple http://localhost:3101/tutorial-simple<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p8"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Restart Apache after this change.</li>
</ul>
<p class="p9"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the vue-deploy.yml for your deployment.</li>
</ul>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Change the parameters for the Deploy to Server step to match where you are deploying.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Most like the REMOTE_HOST and TARGET will change.</li>
</ul>
<p class="p10"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span><span class="s8">env</span>:</p>
<p class="p11"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span></span><span class="s8">SSH_PRIVATE_KEY</span><span class="s2">: </span><span class="s3">${{ </span>secrets<span class="s3">.</span>SERVER_SSH_KEY<span class="s3"> }}</span></p>
<p class="p12"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span></span><span class="s8">ARGS</span><span class="s2">: </span>"-rltgoDzvO --delete"</p>
<p class="p10"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span><span class="s8">SOURCE</span>: <span class="s4">"dist/"</span></p>
<p class="p12"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span></span><span class="s8">REMOTE_HOST</span><span class="s2">: </span>"tutorial.eaglesoftwareteam.com"</p>
<p class="p10"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span><span class="s8">REMOTE_USER</span>: <span class="s1">ubuntu</span></p>
<p class="p12"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span></span><span class="s8">TARGET</span><span class="s2">: </span>"/var/www/html/tutorial-frontend-vue3-simple"</p>
<p class="p2"></p>
<p class="p9"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the vite.config.js</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Update the baseURL for the production directory.</li>
    <li class="li2">Change the “/tutorial-frontend-vue3-simple/” to the directory location in the Apache root for your project.</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p13"><span class="s1">const</span><span class="s2"> </span>baseURL<span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">=</span></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="s2"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span></span><span class="s6">process</span><span class="s2">.</span><span class="s6">env</span><span class="s2">.</span><span class="s7">APP_ENV</span><span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">===</span><span class="s2"> </span>"development"<span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">?</span><span class="s2"> </span>"/"<span class="s2"> </span><span class="s3">:</span><span class="s2"> </span>"/tutorial-frontend-vue3-simple/"<span class="s2">;</span></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p8"><br></p>
<p class="p2">Changes need if using <b>Tutorial-Backend-Simple</b> as starting code</p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the baseurl</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Find app/routes and update all routes files.</li>
    <li class="li2">In each file find the app.use line and<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>replace ‘tutorial-simple’ with the new baseurls</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p14"><span class="s6">app</span><span class="s2">.</span><span class="s9">use</span><span class="s2">(</span>'/tutorial-simple/tutorials'<span class="s2">, </span><span class="s6">router</span><span class="s2">);</span></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the port</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">In the .env file update the port to be the backend port you want to use on your computer.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Change ‘3101’ to the new port number</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p14"><span class="s1">PORT</span><span class="s2">=</span>"3101"</p>
<p class="p15"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the service file tutorial-backend-simple.service</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Update the name of the file to &lt;your project&gt;.service</li>
    <li class="li2">Update the contents of the file and change the<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>project description</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p16">Description=NodeJS Tutorial App Simple</p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Update the contents of the file and change the working directory to the directory for your backend code.</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
<p class="p16">WorkingDirectory=/home/ubuntu/nodeapps/tutorial-backend-simple/</p>
<p class="p9"><br></p>
<ul class="ul1">
  <li class="li2">Update the package.json</li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li2">Update the bundle line.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Change the name of the service file to your service file name.</li>
  </ul>
</ul>
